<h3>Help us improve:</h3>
<p>To send feedback and help us improve this site, <a href="http://www.consumerreports.org/cro/about-us/consumerist-survey/index.htm" target="_blank">please take our survey.</a> We will use this data inform our plans for the future.</p>
<h3>Customer Care:</h3>
<p>Our Customer Care team is happy to help with any general inquiries or concerns, please click here for information on how to contact us, or call us at: 1-800-333-0663 Monday through Friday 8am &#8211; 8pm (EST) and Saturday from 9:30am &#8211; 6pm (EST.)</p>
<h3>Send us a tip:</h3>
<p>To send a tip to our editorial staff, write to tips@consumerist.com.</p>
<p>Please understand that you are contacting journalists and all emails will be considered submissions for publication unless you explicitly request otherwise.</p>
<h3>Press inquiries:</h3>
<p>Members of the media should write to press@consumerist.com</p>
<h3>Consumerist is physically located at:</h3>
<p>Consumer Reports<br />
c/o Consumerist<br />
101 Truman Avenue<br />
Yonkers, NY 10703-1057</p>
